ðŸŒŸ Main Features Introduced in Java 11
1)var for Lambda Parameters
Java 11 allows using var in lambda expressions for local variable type inference.
This helps when you want to add annotations or modifiers to lambda parameters.
Before Java 11, you had to specify the type or leave it inferred without annotations.

Example:
List<String> list = List.of("A", "B", "C");
list.forEach((var s) -> System.out.println(s.toLowerCase()));

2) New String Methods
Java 11 introduced several new methods in String:
isBlank() â†’ checks if string is empty or whitespace
lines() â†’ splits string into lines
strip(), stripLeading(), stripTrailing() â†’ improved trimming
repeat(n) â†’ repeats string n times

Example:
String str = "  Hello  ";
System.out.println(str.isBlank());       // false
System.out.println(str.strip());         // "Hello"
System.out.println("Hi ".repeat(3));     // "Hi Hi Hi "

3)Collection.toArray(IntFunction)
A new toArray(IntFunction<T[]>) method was added to easily convert collections to arrays.

Example:
List<String> list = List.of("Java", "Spring", "Microservices");
String[] arr = list.toArray(String[]::new);
System.out.println(Arrays.toString(arr));

4) Optional.isEmpty()
Optional got a new isEmpty() method â€” opposite of isPresent().
It improves readability when checking absence of a value.

Example:
Optional<String> opt = Optional.empty();
if (opt.isEmpty()) {
    System.out.println("Value is missing!");
}
5) Z Garbage Collector (ZGC)
ZGC is a low-latency garbage collector introduced as an experimental feature in Java 11.
It aims to keep GC pause times below 10ms, even for large heaps (multi-GB).
ZGC works concurrently with application threads, minimizing pause times.

Example (run with flag):
java -XX:+UnlockExperimentalVMOptions -XX:+UseZGC MyApp


Difference between Java 8 and Java 11
---------------------------------------
Java 8 focused on functional programming and Stream API, Lambda expression, Optional classes, Date & Time API.
while Java 11 focused on modern APIs, performance, and developer productivity â€” with new features like the HTTP Client, ZGC, Flight Recorder, Var in Lambda, and enhanced String & File APIs.